CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 3, 1962, pg. C2, reads: "Award Winners - Shown holding awards are (left to right): Daniel G. Kean, Public Relations; James A. Jordon, Industry; Dr. Wilvor C. Waller, Dentistry, and Chester A. Holloway, Job Opportunity."
TitMainTitle: Daniel G. Kean, James Jordon, Wilvor C. Waller, and Chester Holloway, holding awards received during Pittsburgh Courier newspaper's Appreciation Day rally at Soldiers and Sailors Memorial Hall
